  "name": "Characterizing the microbiome of patients with myeloproliferative neoplasms during a Mediterranean diet intervention",
  "author": {
    "name": "Julio Avelar-Barragan",
    "givenName": "Julio",
    "familyName": "Avelar-Barragan",
    "affiliation": {
